WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:05.166
I called you here early this morning

2
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:07.366
because the matter of the dark arts has been investigated.

3
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:08.766
Chun Lan has committed a great crime

4
00:00:09.066 --> 00:00:10.800
by framing Rong Guifei.

5
00:00:10.933 --> 00:00:14.366
Tomorrow, she will be executed by decapitation. The real mastermind is Lin Guiren.

6
00:00:14.366 --> 00:00:16.200
Last night, she has already been punished.

7
00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:18.633
This matter has come to a conclusion.

8
00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:20.233
The truth is revealed.

9
00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:21.566
The truth is now clear.

10
00:00:21.566 --> 00:00:23.900
Your beloved concubine has finally been vindicated.

11
00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:25.100
This time,

12
00:00:25.700 --> 00:00:27.100
I haven’t wronged anyone.

13
00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.300
Rong Guifei did have merit,

14
00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:33.100
but the root of the problem also lies with her.

15
00:00:33.766 --> 00:00:36.066
Your Highness is also a victim.

16
00:00:36.066 --> 00:00:37.366
Don’t forget,

17
00:00:37.366 --> 00:00:40.700
it was because Rong Guifei monopolized your favor

18
00:00:40.866 --> 00:00:43.266
that the other consorts were neglected.

19
00:00:43.866 --> 00:00:46.033
This is what led to this disaster.

20
00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:47.900
Empress Dowager,

21
00:00:47.966 --> 00:00:49.266
I’m feeling a bit unwell.

22
00:00:49.266 --> 00:00:50.366
I’ll excuse myself first.

23
00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.133
Empress Dowager, you’ve gone too far this time.

24
00:00:59.133 --> 00:01:00.666
I still have state affairs to attend to.

25
00:01:00.866 --> 00:01:01.833
I’ll take my leave first.

26
00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:04.300
This is outrageous.

27
00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:06.433
The Emperor is becoming increasingly unreasonable.

28
00:01:06.700 --> 00:01:09.833
Now he dares to confront me like this for Rong Guifei.

29
00:01:11.266 --> 00:01:12.700
Empress Dowager, please calm down.

30
00:01:12.966 --> 00:01:16.233
Indeed, Rong Guifei has been dealt with.

31
00:01:24.766 --> 00:01:26.466
Empress Dowager, may you have peace and prosperity.

32
00:01:35.666 --> 00:01:37.766
Your Highness, who are you angry with?

33
00:01:38.100 --> 00:01:39.866
Isn’t it because of Rong Guifei?

34
00:01:40.466 --> 00:01:43.466
The Emperor is now so infatuated with him

35
00:01:43.533 --> 00:01:46.066
that he dares to defy me.

36
00:01:46.333 --> 00:01:48.900
Sister has suffered such injustice.

37
00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:51.466
Shouldn’t the Emperor try to appease Sister?

38
00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:52.800
The Emperor is now so smitten

39
00:01:52.866 --> 00:01:54.600
that he’d probably give him the stars if asked.

40
00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:57.233
Sister probably doesn’t care for the stars.

41
00:01:57.300 --> 00:01:59.300
After all, you’re already a consort.

42
00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:02.466
Next, the Emperor should be preparing to make Sister Empress.

43
00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:05.600
I cannot let the Emperor make a mess of things.

44
00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:08.566
How can such a person be the mother of a nation?

45
00:02:16.966 --> 00:02:19.400
I see you’re quite suitable.

46
00:02:20.466 --> 00:02:22.833
Don’t jest with me, Your Highness.
